      "title": "Learning guitar with ten focused minutes a day",
      "content": "I used to wait for a perfect one-hour practice window and then skip practice entirely. Ten minutes has been the unlock: tune, warm up, play one chord change slowly, then end with a song I actually like.\n\nThe progress feels tiny day to day, but my fingers are finally doing what my brain asks.",
